{
  "id": "adv_card_mku_02_01",
  "title": "初音ミク 1話 夏休みの宿題？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "すー……はぁ……\nうーん、潮の香りって気持ちいいわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone~!\nThank you so much for coming today!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.8180950324
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "ミクは、どう？　初めての海の感想",
      "translations": {
        "en": "LizNoir Live Tour‚ Hokkaido Performance\nIt was the best time for us too",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.8180950324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.5666680653
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01-mku001.m4a",
      "text": "素敵だね、波の音が清々しい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro's live performance\nOf course you burned it into your eyes‚ right~!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.5666680653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.8850789148
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。その香りも音も忘れられなくなるぐらい\n今日は存分に遊びましょ。ね、すず！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To us‚ and of course to our special guest Miku too\nThank you for your support~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.5666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3877.1444476999973,
          "startTime": 29.4438111144
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.3404984235
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "……え、ええ。そうですわね……\n遊び倒せたら……いいですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you! I had so much fun too!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.1104777811,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.1781659523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "え？　どうしたのよ\nせっかくの海なのに、そんな暗い顔して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's sad to say goodbye‚ but it's finally time to end…\nThank you for coming today——",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、体調でも悪いのか？\nそれなら無理せず休んでいた方が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you very much!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.6124269324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.1601171732
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "い、いえ。体調は問題ないんですの\n問題があるとすれば……その……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good job‚ everyone\nIt was the best live performance",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.3790935991,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.0967610915
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "ご、ごめんなさい！　実はまだ――\n夏休みの宿題、終わっていませんでしたの！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn't that obvious~\nA stage where I stand can't be anything less than the best",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.4457602658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.8179393054
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "え、えぇーー！？\nどうして？　合宿中に終わらせたんじゃなかったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro…\nBut I'm relieved that the audience seemed excited",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.8568320196
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "終わらせるつもりで、頑張っていたんですのよ！？\nでも、ついスマホの誘惑に負けてしまって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you talking like it's someone else's business? You're part of this too\nIt's the result of all our efforts",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.9446531134,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.035607489
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "すずらしくはあるが……海に来て大丈夫だったのか？\n宿題が終わるまで遊ぶのは禁止って話だったんじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right\nToday's live was‚ without flattery‚ something to be proud of",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.0113197801,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.56227448
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "沙季が事情を汲んでくれたんですの\nさすがに一人だけ置いてけぼりはかわいそうだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Miku‚ good job\nThank you so much for performing with us!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.8446531134,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.8064694327
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "なんだ、それなら今は気にせず遊んだっていいじゃない\nもちろん、宿題は後でやらないといけないけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you too!\nLives are really fun‚ aren't they",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.2663106205
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、それは出来ません。なぜなら――\n成宮家の沽券に関わりますもの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ that's right\nEveryone got excited about the new song too",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.5911611395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.2196436486
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "みんなは真面目に宿題を終わらせたからこそ\nこうして遊びに来ているのですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Until we came up with the idea‚ as always\nI was driven crazy by Kokoro…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.9244944729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.752976982
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "私ひとり、お情けで遊ばせてもらおうだなんて\n虫が良過ぎます。フェアじゃありませんわ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well~‚ even you Rio\nYou didn't come up with any good ideas either~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.5911611395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.7545413575
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……なら期日までにちゃんと\n宿題を終わらせれば良かったんじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't deny it… unfortunately…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.9244944729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.0001876754
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "うぐ……や、野暮なツッコミはノーサンキューですわ！\nとにかく。私は決めたのです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But thanks to everyone contributing ideas like that\nWe might have been able to deliver the best song",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.9578278062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "海には行きますわ。けれど……\n宿題が終わるまでは遊ばない、と！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I agree!\nBut aren't you trying to gloss over it~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.2578278062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.0196893931
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 158.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "え……何その拷問みたいな折衷案\nしかも、自分から言い出すって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha… anyway‚ standing here and talking is a bit\nWhy don't we go back to the dressing room and take a break?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それなら、旅館の方が集中出来たんじゃ……\nというか、合宿中にすでに一度海で遊んでたよな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Once we change clothes‚ suddenly\nI feel sad that the live is over",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.8439274625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 169.5431812525
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
